{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stroke-opacity","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-opacity","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>stroke-opacity</code>属性指定了当前对象的轮廓的不透明度。它的默认值是<strong>1</strong>。</p>\n\n<p>作为一个外观属性，它可以直接用作 CSS 样式表内部的属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>&lt;opacity-value&gt; | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/painting.html#StrokeOpacityProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"opacity-value\">&lt;opacity-value&gt;</dt>\n <dd>在当前对象的轮廓上用该涂色操作的不透明度。任何超出 0.0 到 1.0 范围的值都会被压回这个范围（0.0 表示完全透明，1.0 表示完全不透明）。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"svg","title":"SVG","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>120px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>120px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">viewBox</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0 0 120 120<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>rect</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">rect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">fill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>#b4da55<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">stroke</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>#000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">stroke-width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">stroke-opacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>0.3<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"结果\">结果</h3>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-opacity/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>stroke-opacity</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#shape\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Shape\">形状元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#textcontent\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#TextContent\">文本内容元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/fill-opacity\">fill-opacity</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/opacity\">opacity</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stroke-opacity","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stroke-opacity","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stroke-opacity","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stroke-opacity/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-opacity","title":"stroke-opacity"}],"pageTitle":"stroke-opacity - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}